1. **Prešli** smo preko mosta. (We crossed the bridge.)
2. Oni su **prešli** na drugu stranu ulice. (They crossed to the other side of the street.)
3. Kada su **prešli** granicu, bili su srećni što su stigli u novu zemlju. (When they crossed the border, they were happy to have arrived in a new country.)
4. Koliko kilometara ste **prešli** juče? (How many kilometers did you cover yesterday?)
5. Moramo **preći** preko ovog problema pre nego što krenemo dalje. (We need to get over this problem before we move on.)
6. Nadam se da ćemo **preći** na konkretne planove uskoro. (I hope we'll move on to concrete plans soon.)
7. Ako **pređemo** preko mosta, stići ćemo do jezera. (If we cross the bridge, we'll reach the lake.)
8. Oni su **prešli** sa Androida na iPhone. (They switched from Android to iPhone.)